{
  "texts": [
    "One concrete suggestion is to provide \"AI literacy courses\" that have the deliberate intent to foster the associated skills in students.",
    "In order to have a well-rounded and holistic class, an AI literacy program should entail several key components (Kong et al., 2021; Laupichler et al., 2022; Ng et al., 2023c): 1.",
    "Introduction to AI Concepts: Basic definitions and understanding of what AI is, including its history and evolution.",
    "This should cover different types of AI, such as narrow AI, general AI, and superintelligent AI. 2.",
    "Understanding Machine Learning and Technical Foundations: An overview of machine learning, which is a core part of AI."
  ]
}